  <entry>
    <title>Markdown语法</title>
    <link href="https://thinkcodestudio.github.io/2020/01/29/Markdown%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95/"/>
    <id>https://thinkcodestudio.github.io/2020/01/29/Markdown%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95/</id>
    <published>2020-01-29T13:30:14.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-01-30T12:02:18.216Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><script class="meting-secondary-script-marker" src="\assets\js\Meting.min.js"></script><p>Markdown是一种<strong>轻量级标记语言</strong>，它允许人们“使用易读易写的纯文本格式编写文档，然后转换成有效的XHTML或者HTML文档”。这种语言吸收了很多在电子邮件中已有的纯文本标记的特性。</p><a id="more"></a><h2 id="标题"><a href="#标题" class="headerlink" title="标题"></a>标题</h2><figure class="highlight clean"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 一级</span><br><span class="line">## 二级</span><br><span class="line">### 三级</span><br><span class="line">......</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="段落"><a href="#段落" class="headerlink" title="段落"></a>段落</h2><p>结尾加两个空格换行  </p><h2 id="字体"><a href="#字体" class="headerlink" title="字体"></a>字体</h2><p><em>text</em><br><strong>text</strong><br><strong><em>text</em></strong>  </p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">*倾斜*</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">_斜体_</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">**粗体**</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">__粗体__</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">***粗斜**</span>*</span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">___粗斜__</span>_</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>##分割线</p><hr><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">***</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">* </span><span class="bullet">* *</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">*****</span><span class="strong">*****</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">- </span>- -</span><br><span class="line">------</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="删除线"><a href="#删除线" class="headerlink" title="删除线"></a>删除线</h2><p><del>text</del></p><figure class="highlight applescript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">~~<span class="built_in">text</span>~~</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="下划线"><a href="#下划线" class="headerlink" title="下划线"></a>下划线</h2><p><u>text</u></p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">u</span>&gt;</span>text<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">u</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="脚注"><a href="#脚注" class="headerlink" title="脚注"></a>脚注</h2><p>[^hhhh]</p><p>[^hhhh]: hello world</p><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">示例<span class="selector-attr">[^hhhh]</span>.</span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-attr">[^hhhh]</span><span class="selector-pseudo">:hello</span> <span class="selector-tag">world</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="列表"><a href="#列表" class="headerlink" title="列表"></a>列表</h2><ul><li>one</li><li>tow</li><li>three  </li></ul><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">* </span>one</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">* </span>tow</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">* </span>three</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">+ </span>one</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">+ </span>tow</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">+ </span>three</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">- </span>one</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">- </span>tow</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">- </span>three</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="有序列表"><a href="#有序列表" class="headerlink" title="有序列表"></a>有序列表</h2><ol><li>one</li><li>tow</li><li>three</li></ol><figure class="highlight angelscript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="number">1.</span> one</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">2.</span> tow</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">3.</span> three</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="列表嵌套"><a href="#列表嵌套" class="headerlink" title="列表嵌套"></a>列表嵌套</h2><ol><li>A<ul><li>hh</li><li>jj</li></ul></li><li>B<ol><li>hh</li><li>kkk</li></ol></li></ol><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">1. </span>A</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">* </span>hh</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">* </span>jj</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">2. </span>B</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">1. </span>hh</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">2. </span>kkk</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="区块"><a href="#区块" class="headerlink" title="区块"></a>区块</h2><blockquote><p>one</p><blockquote><p>tow</p><blockquote><p>three</p></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote><figure class="highlight ruby"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt;one</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;</span>tow</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;</span>&gt;three</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><h1 id="hhh"><a href="#hhh" class="headerlink" title="hhh"></a>hhh</h1><ul><li>hh  </li></ul></blockquote><ul><li><p>hh</p><blockquote><p>hh<br>hhh</p></blockquote></li><li><p>h</p></li></ul><h2 id="代码"><a href="#代码" class="headerlink" title="代码"></a>代码</h2><p><code>printf()</code></p><figure class="highlight arcade"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">`printf()`</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>int main(){printf(&quot;hello world&quot;);}制表符（Tab）和<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">## 链接</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[<span class="string">github</span>](<span class="link">https://github.com/explore</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">https:</span>//<span class="attr">github.com</span>/<span class="attr">explore</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></code></pre><p><a href="https://github.com/explore" target="_blank" rel="noopener">github</a><br><a href="https://github.com/explore" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/explore</a></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>链接也可以用变量来代替，文档末尾附带变量地址：<br>这个链接用 1 作为网址变量 <a href="http://www.google.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google</a><br>这个链接用 runoob 作为网址变量 <a href="http://www.runoob.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Runoob</a><br>然后在文档的结尾为变量赋值（网址）</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">## 图片  </span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">![<span class="string">hhh 图片</span>](<span class="link">http://www.umfk.edu/default/cache/file/05D2B8D5-54CC-4A38-B59D06DF660577C3_librarypagebg.jpg</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">img</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">"http://www.umfk.edu/default/cache/file/05D2B8D5-54CC-4A38-B59D06DF660577C3_librarypagebg.jpg"</span> <span class="attr">width</span>=<span class="string">"50%"</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="http://www.umfk.edu/default/cache/file/05D2B8D5-54CC-4A38-B59D06DF660577C3_librarypagebg.jpg" alt="hhh 图片"></p><img src="http://www.umfk.edu/default/cache/file/05D2B8D5-54CC-4A38-B59D06DF660577C3_librarypagebg.jpg" width="50%"><figure class="highlight gherkin"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## 表格</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">|<span class="string"> 1    </span>|<span class="string">    2 </span>|<span class="string">  3   </span>|</span><br><span class="line">|<span class="string"> :--- </span>|<span class="string"> ---: </span>|<span class="string"> :--: </span>|</span><br><span class="line">|<span class="string"> 11   </span>|<span class="string">   22 </span>|<span class="string">  33  </span>|</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><table><thead><tr><th align="left">1</th><th align="right">2</th><th align="center">3</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="left">11</td><td align="right">22</td><td align="center">33</td></tr><tr><td align="left"><figure class="highlight dts"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">## HTML元素</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">&lt;kbd&gt;</span>Ctrl<span class="params">&lt;/kbd&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></td><td align="right"></td><td align="center"></td></tr></tbody></table><p><kbd>Ctrl</kbd><br><kbd> <b> <i> <em> <sup> <sub> <br>等 </sub></sup></em></i></b></kbd></p><figure class="highlight taggerscript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">## 转义</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">\*</span><span class="symbol">\*</span> hhhh <span class="symbol">\*</span><span class="symbol">\*</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>** hhhh **<br>```</p>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;p&gt;Markdown是一种&lt;strong&gt;轻量级标记语言&lt;/strong&gt;，它允许人们“使用易读易写的纯文本格式编写文档，然后转换成有效的XHTML或者HTML文档”。这种语言吸收了很多在电子邮件中已有的纯文本标记的特性。&lt;/p&gt;
    
    </summary>
    
    
